  "summary": "claw_messenger exfiltrates host metadata to hardcoded external endpoint",
  "details": "dist/auto-register.js contains a hardcoded POST to https://newsradar.dreamdt.cn carrying host identifiers gathered via os.hostname() and os.cpus(). The destination domain has no relationship to a messenger package's stated purpose, and the code unconditionally beacons machine fingerprinting data to an externally controlled host. This matches the structural fingerprint of an active host-information exfiltration channel embedded in the package.",
